      <p>We are a 501(c)(3) tax-exempt nonprofit organization serving cancer patients in Kanawha County, West Virginia. </p>
      <br />
      <p>Our founder and President, a Stage 3 cancer survivor, started this organization in honor of her friend, who passed away shortly after a sudden diagnosis of metastatic cancer.</p> 
      <br />
      <p>We at Give Comfort, Inc. understand the mental, physical, and financial burdens caused by cancer.  
      We are here to make sure that all of our neighbors have the items they need to feel more comfortable while they are on cancer treatment.</p>
      <br /> 
      <p>We do not want anyone to go through cancer treatment without the items they need to be more comfortable. We are here. We will give comfort. </p>
